import os
import folium
import pandas as pd

m = folium.Map(location=[45.0448400, 38.9760300])
m.choropleth(
    geo_data=mo_gdf[['name_low', 'geometry']].to_json(),
    name='choropleth',
    data=mo_gdf[['name_low','Rate']],
    key_on='feature.properties.name_low',
    columns=['name_low','Rate'],
    fill_color='YlGn',
    line_weight=1,
    fill_opacity=0.7,
    line_opacity=0.2,
    legend_name='type',
    highlight = True
)
